Eir G2 sensor

Price

C$1,026.00

Pre-order and be the first to receive G2, our next generation sensor. G2 will ship later this year. 

 

The first 1,000 customers get lifetime access to our current software features. 

 

Features:

- Slim and discreet - Smaller than the AirPods Pro charging case

- Swim tracking - Water resistant with IPX7

- USB-C for integrated charging, no cradle required

- Adjustable strap - Size the perfect fit for comfort and performance

 

iPhone or iPad with iOS 17 or later required.
